{"tid":784658,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"社交恐懼求救","createTime":"2018-08-18T14:27:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T13:53:12.000Z","uid":195975,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f6b356e7d5569f53fc1eb1294f923a4f82e1e12a","tid":784658,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T14:27:23.000Z","msg":"現實生活中好唔鐘意同人 Social ，特別係多過 3-4個人以上嘅場合，&nbsp;<br />\n開會、聚會、打波會驚到唔想去，作個理由話病呀唔舒服之類唔去。&nbsp;<br />\n除咗最親嘅屋企人、朋友，好驚同陌生人講嘢。&nbsp;<br />\n去七十一麥當勞買嘢都會口疾疾。&nbsp;<br />\n特別見到女仔，我會緊張到耳仔紅，啲汗大滴到會成件衫濕哂。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n就算係虛擬世界入面，幾乎開每一個社交 App ，我都熄哂自動推送 notification，&nbsp;<br />\n例如 Facebook、E-Mail 我每次手動開 App 都要做定心理準備，深呼吸，&nbsp;<br />\n先敢 Click 入去，一掃完，就即刻關咗佢 。&nbsp;<br />\n覆人都要左諗右諗。自己打錯字我直頭會 Del 咗個聊天紀錄，費事眼冤。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n間歇性發作最嚴重嘅時間，我直頭會開飛行模式，用 Wi-Fi 就算，&nbsp;<br />\n因為好驚人會打電話同 Send 短訊俾自己，咁就完全無得避。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n反而主要用嚟聯絡網友嘅 App，好似高登呀，各類非實名嘅 Forum 就無呢個問題 。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n我印象中我細個唔係咁，都幾玩得，吹得，&nbsp;<br />\n係到我中一、中二嘅時候先發現自己開始有呢個問題。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n之後都迫自己要 Social 啲，大膽啲，&nbsp;<br />\n參加好多中學啲咩乜鬼領袖訓練活動、朗誦比賽之類。&nbsp;<br />\n到大學又上莊又住 Hall ，參加球隊咁，但情況都係無咩改善。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n最慘嘅係，我係一個好怕孤獨嘅人，每次我想同人親近，&nbsp;<br />\n但得嚟嘅永遠只有無盡嘅尷尬，同埋不適。&nbsp;<br />\n成個旁觀者咁，睇住人地成班人由唔熟，到一齊玩得好埋好開心。&nbsp;<br />\n自己就投入唔到，形同局外人。心酸到爆！&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n一齊打波，我係會覺得開心嘅。&nbsp;<br />\n但只係一種運動後的滿足感，&nbsp;<br />\n而唔係成 Team 人一齊相處，人際關係上嘅愉悅。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n我自己叫呢種感覺做「強烈的疏離感同抽離感」。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n近呢10年嚟，我就不停係呢個循環入面：&nbsp;<br />\n1. 覺得寂寞，但又驚同人相處&nbsp;<br />\n2. 鼓勵自己，參加嘢、去識人&nbsp;<br />\n3. 老尷、好辛苦&nbsp;<br />\n4. Quit、潛水、中止交往&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n以上文字copy至高登post,因為情況90%相似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,唯一唔同係我中學俾人欺凌之後就開始唔識社交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望各位可以幫下我 唔想一直係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033f612a693929de7b795757013740bb06129c11","tid":784658,"uid":134997,"like":1,"dislike":32,"score":-31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T14:28:03.000Z","msg":"收爹啦 死毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8dcb29fe6d00c6ce42be43ed90a2e2d85a54672","tid":784658,"uid":195975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"033f612a693929de7b795757013740bb06129c11","tid":784658,"uid":134997,"like":1,"dislike":32,"score":-31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T14:28:03.000Z","msg":"收爹啦 死毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T14:38:20.000Z","msg":"我認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc26cbd7f05cb8f57c3106612d0c94a3dbd30f9","tid":784658,"uid":157938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T17:36:08.000Z","msg":"我都有啲類似既經歷<br />\n<br />\n其實有時都要逼一逼自己 <br />\n有啲聚會/ 約實左 <br />\n都要硬住頭皮去 <br />\n<br />\n去買野/ 七仔個啲 試下望多小小人地對眼 <br />\n做完再 review 下 究竟望完人眼 好驚定係咩感覺<br />\n定其實自己係有能力做到 <br />\n如果過到呢關 又要搵其他野挑戰下"},{"pid":"f0f4c5d18e6a636c0e6877ca1875f96ffcb4d4c7","tid":784658,"uid":144323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T17:38:20.000Z","msg":"巴定絲？"},{"pid":"a5230001c65d1df49037e5ef435c359cfe029459","tid":784658,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f0f4c5d18e6a636c0e6877ca1875f96ffcb4d4c7","tid":784658,"uid":144323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T17:38:20.000Z","msg":"巴定絲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:17:18.000Z","msg":"巴"},{"pid":"204b36c09f57b8c64269e35d747ae2985370425a","tid":784658,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T17:32:52.000Z","msg":"完全一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2920b0f0c4f16c6b3ca8a6e51ed541f7c68b3a24","tid":784658,"uid":170083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T17:34:55.000Z","msg":"我都有類似,但未去到咁嚴重"},{"pid":"96949eadc40ac0af227493e56ad0c4182f1016d8","tid":784658,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"204b36c09f57b8c64269e35d747ae2985370425a","tid":784658,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T17:32:52.000Z","msg":"完全一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T07:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b734914479637874b36eb8615401be871c53998","tid":784658,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T11:51:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d582f61fef564fee3734d549185cbdeef6e4744d","tid":784658,"uid":66158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:41:52.000Z","msg":"第一段至第三段我都未去到你咁嚴重 <br />\n但係第四段開始一尻樣 <br />\n由其是你個loop exact7ly<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306f70760113bef243b647b1d8a046fea47b4e4c","tid":784658,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0f4c5d18e6a636c0e6877ca1875f96ffcb4d4c7","tid":784658,"uid":144323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T17:38:20.000Z","msg":"巴定絲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:19:58.000Z","msg":"巴"},{"pid":"ade315149b098573d87b8fee94d68b18e2f2e58b","tid":784658,"uid":61630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T04:16:51.000Z","msg":"一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0048061f4c493b1c68f66c7d23918bf9e00f450","tid":784658,"uid":83095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T22:30:37.000Z","msg":"戒j 腎主恐 我以前都是咁"},{"pid":"6c4ff8db703548429c3afbfa104d7971e74a697a","tid":784658,"uid":161144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T22:37:37.000Z","msg":"same"},{"pid":"0bb5b2fae724bc08e71fc46b7be094975bda3f75","tid":784658,"uid":167186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T22:46:29.000Z","msg":"有懷疑過自己有社交恐懼<br />\n以前唔敢自己買野食 會諗好自己要買咩 係腦入面講幾次要買既野先敢行埋去<br />\n網上買賣有時要約面交 俾錢時手都震埋 <br />\n暑假係屋企唔出門口 落街成日都覺得周圍啲人望緊自己<br />\n有次參加完活動 夜晚成班人搭地鐵 最後得翻我同另一個男仔未到站 佢求其搵話題講 但唔知點解我覺得同佢一齊企好尷尬 feel到自己面紅到落車為止<br />\n後尾覺得咁樣唔掂<br />\n開始迫自己望住人地對眼黎講野<br />\n平時正常傾計應該係望住人地個樣<br />\n但我係focus 係對眼到 咁樣會無咁驚 而已對方又會覺得你望住佢黎講野"},{"pid":"426c26e393c2f2e7e6b4929bfeac537c72160e9c","tid":784658,"uid":156331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T00:48:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2d6e6736b7a9e5bb0bfaa70f4e656febb6da029","tid":784658,"uid":137424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T00:53:58.000Z","msg":"Social Media係一樣好好踏出一步嘅嘢，大家見唔到樣，仲可以搵到興趣相近嘅人吹水。<br />\n我自問都好怕一大班人嘅場合，但又唔抗拒識陌生人，應該只係同內向性格有關。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5476045b366ecd2f45c3cc28121d5027a025ab89","tid":784658,"uid":55375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T01:06:59.000Z","msg":"好少聽怕孤獨<br />\n我幾鍾意獨處"},{"pid":"d0462ec4df875050e9473c1bed9c5d5eec69fcee","tid":784658,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T01:14:41.000Z","msg":"建議你執執個樣，個人會自信啲"},{"pid":"c541475f6d404623daf38b15b956330d25d3eff1","tid":784658,"uid":200286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T01:22:58.000Z","msg":"同我一樣...<br />\n巴打介唔介意留低聯絡方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78e70e9206fe38b8d4c2120be569f75f56b9629d","tid":784658,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T01:40:58.000Z","msg":"腎虧就會細膽，社恐<br />\n戒J一年就會好"},{"pid":"58a8d8f80c37c691818f0005c0d61d36905c1549","tid":784658,"uid":89509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:13:29.000Z","msg":"借pst問一下<br />\n有冇人係之前曾經好有自信<br />\n上台表演完全唔緊張<br />\n但係因為自摺咗半年（因為焦慮症）<br />\n之後同朋友出街會唔舒服、心悸？"},{"pid":"321959a531458e6844a8410a49cbdd42600ed94a","tid":784658,"uid":193077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58a8d8f80c37c691818f0005c0d61d36905c1549","tid":784658,"uid":89509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:13:29.000Z","msg":"借pst問一下<br />\n有冇人係之前曾經好有自信<br />\n上台表演完全唔緊張<br />\n但係因為自摺咗半年（因為焦慮症）<br />\n之後同朋友出街會唔舒服、心悸？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:34:33.000Z","msg":"初時會<br />\n但後期演變成個人好自卑"},{"pid":"8c77c5f80518601ded51a0a05b1b24200d3db00a","tid":784658,"uid":22535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:38:29.000Z","msg":"等住，任何場合你都可以離開，咁就無咁大壓力。"}]}